  "response": "The cost of a 60-minute massage in Houston, TX can vary depending on several factors such as the type of massage, the location of the spa or massage therapist, and any additional services included. On average, a 60-minute massage may range from $60 to $120. Luxury spas or highly specialized therapists may charge more, while promotions or discounts may reduce the price. For the most accurate and up-to-date pricing, it's best to contact local spas and massage therapists directly.",
